Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you really are dead, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you are nothing more than electrical signals running through a computer network,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter who it is challenging me to a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll crush anyone who stands before me, no matter how many times, and press onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll take more than your "Duel of the Creation of Heaven and Earth" to frighten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very well, Noah.\N I accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Invincible Deck Master: Ark of Miracles"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Monsters in the Graveyard are being drawn into the ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my Deck Master's, Miracle of Ark's, Holy Abilities has just been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Abilities...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single card in both of our Graveyards will now be removed from play and stored in the Ark of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, now even your Vampire Lord's Immortal Ability won't be able to activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, keep both of your eyes {\i1}wide open{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the seven turns of the creation of Heaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven turns of the\N creation of Heaven and Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will something happen on the seventh turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is so funny exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to shake me with wondering what will happen on the "seventh turn of creation" won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Flood is a card that destroys all Monster Cards on both players' fields and in their respective hands and Graveyards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that effect, your field is empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both sides have no\N Monsters in their hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This gives me the upper hand if I can Summon a Monster Card before he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the Goddess of Victory smiles on me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Spear Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe\N that attack will get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the second Ability of my Deck Master, Ark of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, being chosen by the ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Lord...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Ability of the Ark of Miracles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Absolute Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my opponent holds more Monsters than I at the start of their Battle Phase, I can call out a Monster at random in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Dragon inflicts damage to the opponent equally the difference in their Attack and Defense Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least he was able to scratch Noah's Life a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter how many Monsters Kaiba has out on the field, he'll always have something to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really totally untouchable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the second turn of creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's about to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The water...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's evaporating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into something really strange, OOH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following that, the Earth entered the age of the dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Giant Rex!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Rex, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Dragon is a card that automatically changes into Defense Position after attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that Effect, your Life Points remain unchanged, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, I said this right from the beginning, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That my very existence is superior to you in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I lost my flesh-and-blood body, my conscious has lived in inside of this super computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of the computer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Noah is really dead, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have been {\i1}resurrected{\i0} from the abyss of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a being that exceeds\N any one of your imaginations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know how to\N deal with it in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I soon became surprised at how comfortable it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't boring in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because there's a hoard of information from the Human World stored within this realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how thick a book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how complicated a set of data that would take an ordinary human several hours to absorb may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My computer-like brain can register it in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, I have learned everything there is to know about the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned about everything dating back to when the universe was first born all the way to present world history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no human brain in existence that knows as much as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, there is a {\i1}huge{\i0} difference\nbetween {\i1}your{\i0} brain and {\i1}mine{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were nothing more than a test given to me by Father so that I would become equal to that of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Noah say Kaiba was a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creation of Heaven and Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The age of mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about as\N much as I can take from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened to you in your past has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But regardless of what you think you are, you're about as human as you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because all that ridiculous self-praising and arrogance is nothing more than an excuse to seal away your heart from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what any foolish human being who is too absorbed in themselves would try and do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can shake me with such childish insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then answer this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Gozaburo really intended for you to inherit Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't he just give it to you and let you compete against me openly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he choose direct methods?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you feel it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Gozaburo couldn't trust his future into someone like you, a trapped being inside an AI Computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was certain that I was hit by a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it! That was all a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father! Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father! Please let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why not, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, listen to me carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You aren't able to leave that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your body... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But your spirit is still very well alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to touch you with my hands, but the fact that you are my son will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... dead...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a gift from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father gradually expanded the world I lived in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He added the data of places I wanted to travel one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good morning, Noah-{\i0}sama{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why hello there, Noah-{\i0}sama{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world is so delicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Noah-sama.\N What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sure is a nice day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Noah-sama.\N What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Noah-sama.\N What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Noah-sama.\N What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get lost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you like the birthday present\nthat I gave it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never thought I'd get to travel into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna show you how blue the Earth is-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah, you saw the data when you uploaded it for me, so you saw exactly what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, where is Sunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a few modifications to him/ Now he's really rabid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Modifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a muzzle that locks up his face so he doesn't bite anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one you had before was no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The program was too simple.\N I had to remake him from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a simulation of something interesting not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I calculated that if we used the entire financial resources and weaponry of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we could destroy the entire world in just 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh... But how many people would survive after this plan of yours was commenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About 3%, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think that's a bit too little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't really care.\N It has nothing to do with me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have already surpassed the level of human thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've started to see a {\b0}much{\b1} larger perspective of Kaiba Corporation now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It does intrigue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'll listen to it some other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't long after that you entered the Kaiba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how much information I had to offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father began to\N stop coming to visit me altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes to show that even someone like Gozaburo has some sense of human conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can see is this invented world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But human society exists in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is weaved by both light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the feelings of those who struggle for the strength to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only someone who has lived in the world would be able to comprehend those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gozaburo probably started to become confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then after that he came up with the idea of having you compete with a real flesh-and-blood human being - me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could win a competition against a real human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would have been able to accept you and all of your knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have thought like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost every important aspect a human being needs while living in that cold world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost my feelings as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have {\i1}surpassed{\i0} them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of walking down\N the path of a creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a "creator" just because you invented this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really makes me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to prove once and for all that I am now the creator of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make a prediction in the name of "creator".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the third turn of creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an event will occur that will shock the very core of your existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock the... very {\i1}core of my existence{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn will end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card, Pot of Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Effect allows me to draw two more cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate\N Kaiser Sea Horse's Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He allows me to Summon a Light-Attribute Monster without the need of a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I can Summon the Level 5 Twilight Zone Dragon without a tribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also place three set cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that will end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good! Noah's Giant Rex has 2000 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's Monster will be destroyed next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he tries to Summon another Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least one of those Set Cards must be intended to cancel a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you were never qualified to be my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the result of this match will be decided this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card known as Deepest Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, OOH-AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun was swallowed in a cloud of residue, as per the result of a large meteor shower that bombarded the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, mankind welcomed the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His own Monster was destroyed thanks to his Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deepest Impact destroys\N every Monster on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Life of both players is halved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's... not going to attack my Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Ice Age Panic Magic Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be activated when I have no Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me Special Summon an Earth-Attribute Monster to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Summon Last of Tusk Mammoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Twilight Zone Dragon, come back to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight Zone Dragon holds an Effect that gives him the ability to travel through dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the Magic Card you used before didn't work on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be destroyed in battle, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read through your plan to use that slaughtering Magic Card right from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Last of Tusk Mammoth, attack Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he seriously gonna attack a Monster with higher Defense Points, OOH~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the Ability of the Twilight Zone Dragon from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I'm certain you're aware of {\i1}Last of Tusk Mammoth's{\i0} Ability, {\i1}right{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last of Tusk Mammoth's Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,takes the damage it receives and shifts it to the opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's taking 700 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} only has 700 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card! Destruction Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction Ring destroys our Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and both sides take the damage to their Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only be blowing {\i1}yourself{\i0} up with this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Instant Quick-Summon Magic Card, Defense Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaiba for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned the situation against his enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you superior to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more attack will determine the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Noah's Monster Barrier hasn't been broken yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, I'll settle things on this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I anticipate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Twilight Zone Dragon from Defense Mode to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then eliminate Thunder Dragon from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Thunder Dragon's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ca add two more of the card from my deck into my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Twin-Headed Thunder Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2800 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate the Magic Card, Quick Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to its effect, a Fusion Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can attack on the turn it is Summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you increase the number of Monsters you hold, it's all futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, chosen beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Monsters appeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our result was decided just now, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that your Deck Master is the strongest and is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my Dueling intellect far surpasses yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last trap I set for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate now, Dragon's Imperial Wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Dragon's Imperial Wrath's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I attack a Defense Monster with less Defense Points than my Monster's Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opponent receives the difference in value as direct damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Giant Rex!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another monster down and Kaiba will be the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my sight, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Headed Thunder Dragon, attack Giant Soldier of-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who dares to hurt my big brother. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Save me, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} the one bullying {\i1}me{\i0} here! He's our {\i1}enemy{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that fact that you had the misfortune of having your little brother's memory sealed away by me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba now thinks of me as his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba protects me of his free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, you know, Mokuba is my {\i1}little brother{\i0} and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can defeat me with one more attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything rides on your shoulders right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow me away along with Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I predicted this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That something would happen this turn that would shock the very core of your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Noah anticipated\N that he would make it this far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry up and attack me, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} blocks Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s path in order to protect Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Noah's prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to beat Noah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is impossible for Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}\nto attack Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah attacks Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient!\nKaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way to recall Mokuba-kun's memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save Mokuba! The Fateful Seventh Turn"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
